    <h1 id="avatar">Avatar</h1>
    <p>
        Avatar is a picture or component used to identify a user. <br>
        Use classes in format <span class="example-in-article">"avatar-size"</span> to get avatar of
        required size.
        For example - "avatar-sm" for small size avatar.
    </p>
    <div class="component__container">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/72" alt="" class="avatar-xs">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/72" alt="" class="avatar-sm">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/72" alt="" class="avatar-md">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/72" alt="" class="avatar-lg">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/72" alt="" class="avatar-xl">
    </div>

